WEBVTT

01:36.979 --> 01:40.960
[The Best Thing]

01:41.479 --> 01:48.770
[Episode 18: Acorus Calamus: pungent and bitter in taste, warm in nature, opens the orifices, dispels phlegm, awakens the mind, enhances intelligence, resolves dampness, and stimulates the appetite]

01:48.970 --> 01:50.330
[Signing Ceremony]

01:51.160 --> 01:52.610
It's almost time.

01:52.640 --> 01:54.030
I think it's almost over.

01:54.120 --> 01:55.789
Arrange the shuttles in advance.

01:55.820 --> 01:56.789
Don't waste time.

01:56.810 --> 01:57.470
Okay, Manager.

01:57.490 --> 01:58.490
I'll head over now.

01:58.520 --> 01:59.330
Okay, go ahead.

01:59.350 --> 01:59.990
I'll leave it to you.

02:13.180 --> 02:14.250
The weather is nice today.

02:20.280 --> 02:21.360
Mr. Yan, look over here!

02:21.360 --> 02:22.520
Mr. Yan, over here!

02:24.630 --> 02:25.880
Mr. Yan, over here!

02:28.310 --> 02:29.630
Mr. Yan, look over here!

03:01.070 --> 03:02.720
See you later.

03:47.790 --> 03:48.510
What's wrong, Dad?

03:48.990 --> 03:49.820
Did you see the news?

03:51.040 --> 03:53.250
The signing ceremony went well.

03:55.240 --> 03:56.000
Of course.

03:57.810 --> 03:59.560
Now that the cooperation is settled, you can come back.

04:00.060 --> 04:01.620
Don't waste time in Hang City.

04:04.600 --> 04:05.880
I'll handle it myself.

04:06.910 --> 04:09.500
You're marrying Shen Xifan to go against me.

04:09.820 --> 04:11.270
Don't you think that's childish?

04:12.310 --> 04:14.270
With your little achievements now,

04:14.270 --> 04:15.150
you really think

04:15.150 --> 04:17.220
you've fully established yourself in this industry?

04:17.829 --> 04:18.839
I've already said

04:19.310 --> 04:20.829
that I'll handle it myself.

04:21.660 --> 04:22.180
Alright.

04:23.180 --> 04:26.070
I'd like to see what you can actually achieve.

04:52.950 --> 04:54.540
Unit 7, Room 502?

04:54.540 --> 04:55.040
Yes.

04:55.890 --> 04:56.770
What's the owner's last name?

04:56.790 --> 04:57.440
Shen.

04:58.960 --> 04:59.640
Yes.

05:00.180 --> 05:00.830
Please come in.

05:01.780 --> 05:02.830
Mr. Yan, it's done.

05:24.420 --> 05:25.000
Ms. Liu,

05:26.950 --> 05:29.910
I saw Yan on the public account of the hotel

05:32.450 --> 05:33.820
where Ms. Shen is working.

05:38.710 --> 05:39.830
It really is him.

05:41.030 --> 05:42.070
What is this?

05:43.159 --> 05:44.840
Their company

05:45.430 --> 05:47.510
is holding an event at Gunan Huating Hotel?

05:49.540 --> 05:51.300
Why didn't Ms. Shen tell us?

05:51.780 --> 05:52.630
I knew it.

05:52.630 --> 05:54.860
She's been in a really bad mood lately.

05:56.370 --> 05:58.070
How long has Yan been back?

06:00.210 --> 06:01.960
It's him, right? Look at this photo.

06:02.020 --> 06:02.780
Definitely.

06:11.640 --> 06:12.710
Where are you going?

06:13.270 --> 06:14.180
To get some spicy hot pot.

06:15.680 --> 06:17.340
You still have the mood to eat spicy hot pot?

06:17.510 --> 06:18.950
Your house is on fire.

06:19.480 --> 06:20.360
Are you kidding me?

06:20.390 --> 06:21.760
I just left my house.

06:21.790 --> 06:22.870
Look.

06:27.030 --> 06:27.820
Chen Qiang?

06:27.860 --> 06:28.350
Yes.

06:28.740 --> 06:29.910
Just now, someone who looked

06:29.910 --> 06:31.470
really rich and powerful

06:31.500 --> 06:33.260
went to Shen's house to propose marriage.

06:34.270 --> 06:37.370
Did he look like a boss?

06:37.420 --> 06:38.210
Yes.

06:39.940 --> 06:40.500
Thank you.

06:46.670 --> 06:47.790
Mr. Yan, everything's here.

06:49.500 --> 06:50.870
Hello, Mr. and Mrs. Shen.

06:51.200 --> 06:51.990
Long time no see.

06:52.150 --> 06:53.150
Yes, yes.

06:54.020 --> 06:55.050
What would you like to drink?

06:55.070 --> 06:55.720
I...

06:56.100 --> 06:58.150
I remember you like coffee, right?

06:58.150 --> 06:59.830
No need to trouble yourself, Mr. Shen. I'll just have some water.

07:00.190 --> 07:01.220
You can make do with that?

07:02.410 --> 07:03.530
Please, have a seat.

07:03.640 --> 07:04.520
Thank you, Mr. Shen.

07:09.140 --> 07:10.060
Well,

07:10.150 --> 07:11.470
it's been a while

07:11.500 --> 07:12.870
since I heard from you.

07:13.660 --> 07:15.360
I was busy with my startup last year.

07:15.940 --> 07:18.460
Fortunately, the company is doing well now,

07:18.860 --> 07:19.740
and we've won some awards.

07:20.150 --> 07:21.150
I came back this time

07:21.180 --> 07:22.270
mainly to handle

07:22.270 --> 07:23.970
the company's move to the tech park.

07:24.340 --> 07:26.340
I just came back from the signing ceremony this afternoon

07:26.460 --> 07:27.990
and rushed over to see you.

07:41.510 --> 07:42.300
Oh, right, Mr. and Mrs. Shen,

07:42.300 --> 07:43.909
I brought some gifts for you from abroad.

07:43.909 --> 07:44.980
Let me open them and show you.

07:44.980 --> 07:46.300
Yan, sit first.

07:51.700 --> 07:52.620
Well, Yan,

07:53.710 --> 07:55.070
what do you mean by this?

07:56.710 --> 07:58.540
I think the breakup last year

07:58.680 --> 07:59.570
must have

08:00.340 --> 08:01.980
made you and Xifan

08:01.980 --> 08:02.980
feel uncomfortable.

08:04.150 --> 08:05.270
But I came back this time

08:05.270 --> 08:06.830
to get back together with Xifan.

08:07.400 --> 08:08.840
When the time is right, we'll get married.

08:12.340 --> 08:13.150
The breakup happened

08:13.150 --> 08:14.180
partly because

08:15.180 --> 08:16.910
I was too busy at the time,

08:17.100 --> 08:18.100
and partly because

08:18.360 --> 08:19.980
I didn't come to terms with it

08:20.100 --> 08:21.250
and didn't want her to study abroad.

08:21.860 --> 08:23.420
That's what led to where we are now.

08:24.020 --> 08:25.220
But I've come to terms with it.

08:25.590 --> 08:26.740
Letting her study abroad

08:26.740 --> 08:27.980
and broaden her horizons is a good thing.

08:29.740 --> 08:32.419
Nowadays, going abroad isn't that hard.

08:32.460 --> 08:33.350
If she wants to go to any school,

08:33.350 --> 08:34.419
I can arrange it right away.

08:35.429 --> 08:37.500
We've been together for seven years,

08:38.030 --> 08:39.720
and taking some time apart

08:39.789 --> 08:41.669
could actually help our relationship in the long run.

08:43.700 --> 08:44.990
Besides, we know each other so well.

08:44.990 --> 08:46.510
We're a perfect match for marriage.

08:47.940 --> 08:49.750
Aren't you staying at Xifan's hotel?

08:50.150 --> 08:52.070
Why didn't she come back with you?

08:54.100 --> 08:55.890
Does she know you're here?

08:58.390 --> 08:59.960
Is marriage a one-person thing?

09:00.870 --> 09:02.510
Do you know what Xifan thinks?

09:05.460 --> 09:06.660
Mrs. Shen, please don't get angry.

09:07.580 --> 09:08.420
Of course I know

09:08.420 --> 09:10.180
it's not easy to get back with Xifan,

09:10.440 --> 09:12.590
but I will do my best.

09:13.000 --> 09:15.240
Besides, you don't really know what happened between us.

09:15.780 --> 09:18.110
The breakup happened because Xifan made a mistake first.

09:18.670 --> 09:20.000
I never mentioned it, did I?

09:20.770 --> 09:22.450
This time, I'm here with sincerity.

09:24.210 --> 09:25.660
What are you doing in my house?

09:26.780 --> 09:27.420
Visiting your parents.

09:27.420 --> 09:28.040
What's wrong?

09:28.070 --> 09:29.470
Visiting my parents?

09:29.940 --> 09:30.920
What do you want to say?

09:31.200 --> 09:32.740
You want me to marry you?

09:32.930 --> 09:34.840
What do you want me to do to make you happy?

09:35.110 --> 09:36.670
Have you ever cared about my feelings?

09:36.780 --> 09:37.490
Well, have you...

09:38.350 --> 09:39.700
Have you ever cared about my feelings?

09:41.460 --> 09:42.820
I'm begging for your forgiveness.

09:42.840 --> 09:43.440
What about you?

09:43.950 --> 09:44.980
You just keep avoiding me,

09:45.010 --> 09:46.820
making me look like a fool, searching for you everywhere.

09:47.840 --> 09:49.480
Like a fool?

09:50.270 --> 09:51.230
When we broke up,

09:51.230 --> 09:53.030
wasn't this how you treated me?

09:53.840 --> 09:55.580
When we broke up, you sent me a message

09:55.580 --> 09:57.560
and then disappeared, Yan Heng.

09:58.770 --> 10:00.650
Do you know how much I wanted to find you

10:00.700 --> 10:02.670
and how much I wanted you to reply to my message?

10:02.850 --> 10:03.660
At that time,

10:03.660 --> 10:05.580
I would've gone back to you like a dog,

10:05.580 --> 10:06.940
apologizing obediently.

10:08.400 --> 10:09.830
But where were you?

10:17.370 --> 10:18.730
Why is there someone else here?

10:22.420 --> 10:23.180
Mr. Shen, Mrs. Shen.

10:25.780 --> 10:27.660
This is the medicinal soup I made.

10:27.770 --> 10:29.060
But it's for four people.

10:30.080 --> 10:31.310
I'm not sure if it's enough for all of us.

10:33.800 --> 10:34.640
Here, take it.

10:40.120 --> 10:40.800
Xifan.

10:53.290 --> 10:54.000
Xifan.

10:55.360 --> 10:56.450
Do you hate me so much now

10:56.480 --> 10:57.750
because you've fallen for him?

11:02.420 --> 11:03.030
What could a poor TCM physician

11:03.030 --> 11:03.780
give you?

11:03.780 --> 11:04.490
And what about you?

11:05.070 --> 11:06.540
Besides some stupid money,

11:07.000 --> 11:08.290
what can you give her?

11:09.860 --> 11:11.030
Listen carefully.

11:12.030 --> 11:13.110
Only those who have nothing to offer

11:13.110 --> 11:14.200
would say something like this.

11:20.820 --> 11:21.570
Yan Heng,

11:22.580 --> 11:24.510
please get out of my house.

11:25.060 --> 11:25.480
Mr. Shen...

11:25.510 --> 11:27.030
No one here welcomes you!

11:29.620 --> 11:30.790
Get out now!

11:56.000 --> 11:57.640
You only care about yourself,

11:58.150 --> 11:59.790
never considering how others feel.

12:18.120 --> 12:19.480
Working at the hotel,

12:19.510 --> 12:20.980
you should keep a professional attitude

12:21.080 --> 12:22.360
and keep your distance from the customers.

12:22.520 --> 12:24.300
Wasn't this part of your training when you just started working here?

12:26.330 --> 12:28.290
Am I working this hard for myself?

12:28.760 --> 12:30.230
What exactly are you dissatisfied with?

12:30.600 --> 12:31.900
How can you be so willful?

12:32.940 --> 12:33.940
Do you know how much trouble

12:33.940 --> 12:35.700
your willfulness has caused everyone?

12:35.960 --> 12:37.410
Who can stand you?

12:44.830 --> 12:46.270
Do you want to see how sad and hurt

12:46.300 --> 12:48.180
he can be for you?

12:48.200 --> 12:50.000
Or do you just want to prove how charming you are?

12:50.550 --> 12:52.400
Why aren't you wearing socks in this cold weather?

12:52.750 --> 12:53.910
Senior He has always been

12:53.910 --> 12:55.870
a very gentle and kind person.

12:56.230 --> 12:56.910
But that doesn't mean

12:56.910 --> 12:58.630
you can treat him so casually.

12:59.070 --> 13:00.590
You don't deserve him at all.

13:06.510 --> 13:08.200
It's all my fault.

13:10.650 --> 13:12.410
It's all my fault.

13:47.060 --> 13:47.940
Xifan,

13:53.220 --> 13:54.150
you did nothing wrong.

14:49.360 --> 14:50.880
It was my fault today.

14:52.820 --> 14:55.350
I shouldn't have opened the door for Yan.

14:59.740 --> 15:01.900
How dare he come to our house?

15:04.660 --> 15:06.750
How did he treat Xifan

15:06.940 --> 15:08.250
when they broke up?

15:10.580 --> 15:12.700
How dare he sit here, shamelessly saying

15:12.700 --> 15:13.990
he wants to marry her?

15:17.300 --> 15:17.870
Alright, alright.

15:17.870 --> 15:19.940
Don't be so angry.

15:20.710 --> 15:22.830
Now that we have clarified everything today,

15:22.860 --> 15:24.340
it'll be fine from now on.

15:25.350 --> 15:27.510
Did you hear what Xifan said today?

15:28.050 --> 15:28.640
Yes.

15:29.230 --> 15:30.800
It broke my heart.

15:34.540 --> 15:35.910
When Xifan broke up with him,

15:36.630 --> 15:37.800
he treated her that way.

15:37.940 --> 15:39.580
She came home without saying a word,

15:39.940 --> 15:41.030
keeping it from us.

15:41.750 --> 15:43.030
She couldn't sleep every night,

15:43.030 --> 15:44.180
suffering from insomnia,

15:44.180 --> 15:45.540
and looked so exhausted.

15:46.420 --> 15:47.590
She must have been

15:47.870 --> 15:49.630
heartbroken inside.

15:53.940 --> 15:54.870
After that,

15:55.480 --> 15:56.970
I arranged blind dates for her,

15:57.630 --> 15:58.950
constantly asking her

15:58.980 --> 16:00.360
to do this and that.

16:00.660 --> 16:02.180
I'm her mother.

16:02.180 --> 16:03.870
What did I do?

16:06.050 --> 16:08.400
She was thinking of us.

16:15.500 --> 16:16.910
During the New Year,

16:18.240 --> 16:19.850
she seemed to be feeling better.

16:20.760 --> 16:21.930
But then things went wrong again.

16:23.440 --> 16:25.350
I noticed it at the time,

16:25.710 --> 16:27.380
but I didn't think to call Lin

16:27.400 --> 16:28.280
and Ya.

16:28.960 --> 16:30.680
If I had called them,

16:31.040 --> 16:33.280
she wouldn't have been so sad, right?

16:39.400 --> 16:40.030
Come on.

16:40.030 --> 16:40.580
Alright, alright.

16:40.580 --> 16:41.460
Don't be angry.

16:41.460 --> 16:42.540
Let me give you a massage.

16:52.120 --> 16:53.090
Feeling better?

16:54.380 --> 16:55.220
Yes.

17:39.430 --> 17:40.240
What are you looking at?

17:41.110 --> 17:42.070
Clean it up!

17:48.560 --> 17:49.520
What's going on?

17:50.870 --> 17:52.080
Mr. Yan is drunk

17:52.180 --> 17:53.620
and smashed everything.

17:56.550 --> 17:57.340
Mr. Yan,

17:57.940 --> 17:59.790
you'll have to compensate for everything you damaged.

17:59.820 --> 18:00.450
Get lost.

18:05.500 --> 18:06.460
What now?

18:07.260 --> 18:08.260
I said I'm not going back!

18:08.260 --> 18:09.590
Take photos and videos of everything,

18:09.610 --> 18:11.020
and go to the finance department tomorrow to assess the damages.

18:11.040 --> 18:12.040
Leave me alone.

18:12.740 --> 18:13.930
Leave me alone!

18:22.750 --> 18:23.590
Xifan.

18:24.140 --> 18:25.040
Senior Lin,

18:25.340 --> 18:27.230
I took a day off tomorrow.

18:27.250 --> 18:30.090
Please keep an eye on the situation in the housekeeping division for me.

18:30.120 --> 18:31.800
Call me if anything happens.

18:32.100 --> 18:33.170
Okay, no problem.

18:33.340 --> 18:34.470
It's Friday tomorrow.

18:34.700 --> 18:36.040
Take a good rest these days.

18:36.170 --> 18:37.560
Don't think about anything. Just relax.

18:38.740 --> 18:39.540
Thank you.

18:39.960 --> 18:40.620
Bye.

19:00.500 --> 19:01.150
Come in.

19:04.910 --> 19:05.870
You're up?

19:14.520 --> 19:15.950
He sent you some medicine.

19:15.970 --> 19:17.260
He said it's for calming your nerves

19:17.310 --> 19:18.550
and asked you to drink it while it's hot.

19:21.070 --> 19:21.740
Okay.

19:22.350 --> 19:23.390
I'll drink it soon.

19:34.550 --> 19:36.990
Why do you have to bear everything on your own?

19:41.180 --> 19:43.070
Why didn't you tell us when you were hurt?

19:47.430 --> 19:48.810
You even lied to us,

19:50.070 --> 19:51.420
saying it was a peaceful breakup.

19:53.010 --> 19:55.050
But you suffered a lot.

19:57.350 --> 19:58.700
Didn't it hurt?

20:05.510 --> 20:06.300
I'll say no more.

20:08.720 --> 20:10.800
I didn't want you to worry.

20:17.480 --> 20:19.480
But we are your family.

20:23.460 --> 20:24.590
Remember,

20:25.870 --> 20:27.840
no matter how old you are,

20:28.260 --> 20:29.910
in your dad and my eyes,

20:30.350 --> 20:32.020
you're always just a kid.

20:38.220 --> 20:39.700
I didn't do it on purpose.

20:40.530 --> 20:43.600
I thought I could handle it myself.

20:54.700 --> 20:56.260
From now on, no matter what happens,

20:56.990 --> 20:58.380
you mustn't hide it from us.

20:58.600 --> 20:59.440
Got it?

21:06.880 --> 21:08.250
Yes.

21:11.590 --> 21:13.010
Sent it to the headquarters of Zhongyu Tech, right?

21:13.040 --> 21:13.550
Yes.

21:13.810 --> 21:15.010
The name is Yan Heng, right?

21:15.040 --> 21:15.880
Yes.

21:15.910 --> 21:16.660
Okay, thank you.

21:54.360 --> 21:56.730
Did you brew today's medicine?

21:57.940 --> 21:59.420
It smells fresh.

22:07.770 --> 22:08.440
Yes.

22:09.180 --> 22:10.350
It's for relieving anxiety and calming the nerves.

22:11.350 --> 22:12.870
I specially added acorus calamus for you.

22:29.260 --> 22:32.420
♫A light scent♫

22:30.710 --> 22:31.690
I took a sip.

22:36.880 --> 22:41.120
♫Slowly awakening my heart♫

22:41.610 --> 22:45.790
♫The elusive little mist appears and disappears♫

22:46.700 --> 22:53.290
♫Quietly entering your world, your memories♫

22:52.180 --> 22:54.710
Drink the medicine and take a nap.

22:54.650 --> 22:57.540
♫The unexpected encounter with the wind♫

22:55.790 --> 22:58.180
When you wake up, everything will get better.

23:00.470 --> 23:05.080
♫Layer by layer, rendering the air♫

23:06.900 --> 23:11.260
♫The whispers that are sometimes far, sometimes near♫

23:11.770 --> 23:17.160
♫Exchanging our hidden secrets♫

23:18.780 --> 23:24.050
♫Using my breath♫

23:25.060 --> 23:31.100
♫To blend the soothing scent of love♫

23:31.430 --> 23:34.240
♫To merge in♫

23:36.990 --> 23:40.020
♫The air♫

23:43.720 --> 23:48.260
♫Shortens the distance between two hearts♫

23:51.210 --> 23:54.680
♫Longing adjusts its frequency♫

23:57.300 --> 24:02.040
♫Resonating with our expectations♫

24:03.560 --> 24:07.650
♫The little challenges that time has given us♫

24:08.520 --> 24:13.750
♫Are meant to deepen the meaning of loving you♫

24:15.520 --> 24:20.790
♫Using my breath♫

24:21.800 --> 24:27.840
♫To blend the soothing scent of love♫

24:28.050 --> 24:30.860
♫To merge in♫

24:33.870 --> 24:37.260
♫The air♫

24:40.550 --> 24:43.870
♫It's you who always follow me♫

24:45.310 --> 24:46.220
Is it done?

24:46.220 --> 24:47.500
Yes.

24:50.180 --> 24:51.350
Time to eat.

24:52.860 --> 24:54.340
Have a seat. Don't be shy.

24:56.390 --> 24:57.950
Thank you for coming

24:58.350 --> 24:59.660
to keep our Ms. Shen company.

25:00.180 --> 25:01.710
Mr. Shen, you don't need to be so polite with us.

25:01.910 --> 25:03.150
Alright, I won't.

25:03.640 --> 25:04.600
Right, Mrs. Shen?

25:04.660 --> 25:05.460
Yes, that's right.

25:05.480 --> 25:07.040
Don't be polite with us either.

25:07.350 --> 25:09.220
Come over for dinner whenever you have time.

25:09.900 --> 25:11.940
It's the first time I've seen you two after the New Year.

25:12.590 --> 25:14.620
Your uncle has learned to make medicated dishes now,

25:14.650 --> 25:15.930
and they taste pretty good.

25:16.110 --> 25:16.660
Try some.

25:16.980 --> 25:18.660
Xiangya, aren't you a food critic?

25:18.790 --> 25:19.710
Give us a review.

25:19.730 --> 25:20.770
Oh, okay.

25:22.360 --> 25:23.400
Medicinal dishes, huh?

25:28.940 --> 25:29.790
Oh, right.

25:29.810 --> 25:30.850
Thank you, Mrs. Shen.

25:31.970 --> 25:33.780
Let me tell you something funny.

25:33.870 --> 25:36.550
Yesterday, Yan Heng went back to his room and caused a scene,

25:36.550 --> 25:37.700
smashing everything.

25:37.700 --> 25:39.150
We assessed the damage this morning,

25:39.170 --> 25:40.880
and it's going to cost a lot to compensate.

25:42.020 --> 25:43.070
He told me

25:43.070 --> 25:45.790
that his dad scolded him terribly because of this.

25:46.710 --> 25:48.100
Even Mr. Yan knows about this?

25:48.510 --> 25:50.180
Why did he make such a big scene?

25:50.500 --> 25:51.630
It was mainly embarrassing.

25:51.790 --> 25:53.750
After all, he's the boss of a company now.

25:53.780 --> 25:55.210
Getting drunk and causing a scene

25:55.690 --> 25:57.130
is a bad influence.

25:58.550 --> 26:01.470
What was his original check-out date?

26:01.500 --> 26:02.130
Wednesday.

26:02.640 --> 26:04.440
Oh right, the General Manager talked to me today,

26:04.510 --> 26:06.070
saying that he plans to refuse his extension

26:06.090 --> 26:07.160
after it expires.

26:08.110 --> 26:09.630
He is a VIP customer.

26:09.630 --> 26:10.870
Is the General Manager really willing to do that?

26:11.310 --> 26:12.110
If the General Manager

26:12.110 --> 26:13.070
heard you say that,

26:13.070 --> 26:14.500
he'd definitely be upset again.

26:15.070 --> 26:16.870
This was something he brought up himself.

26:16.870 --> 26:19.600
He said Yan Heng has a bad personality,

26:19.830 --> 26:21.710
has gone too far,

26:21.740 --> 26:22.890
and is too difficult to deal with.

26:27.390 --> 26:28.760
Let's stop talking about this.

26:29.220 --> 26:31.420
Remember to treat your General Manager to a meal

26:31.460 --> 26:33.330
to thank him for his concern.

26:33.580 --> 26:35.140
And bring these two with you

26:35.160 --> 26:36.250
so you can have fun together.

26:36.530 --> 26:38.290
Don't worry. Thank you.

26:38.320 --> 26:39.120
Eat more today.

26:40.240 --> 26:42.760
Today's full of good news.

26:43.500 --> 26:45.020
We can have a little wine.

26:45.270 --> 26:47.030
-Why do you always find excuses to drink?
-Mr. Shen.

26:47.060 --> 26:48.650
Come on. It's the weekend.

26:48.670 --> 26:50.410
I don't have class tomorrow.

26:50.440 --> 26:52.810
It's fine. I'll have a drink with Mr. Shen.

26:52.830 --> 26:53.910
-Great.
-Xiangya.

26:53.910 --> 26:55.150
That's great, Xiangya.

26:55.150 --> 26:56.020
Just a little.

26:56.020 --> 26:56.980
Don't drink a couple of glasses with Mr. Shen

26:56.980 --> 26:57.940
and then turn into this:

26:57.940 --> 26:58.980
Cheers, Mr. Shen!

26:59.910 --> 27:00.500
Here.

27:00.500 --> 27:01.910
This is for Xiangya.

27:01.910 --> 27:03.350
Thank you, Mrs. Shen.

27:03.790 --> 27:04.420
Shut up.

27:05.860 --> 27:07.090
I have an announcement to make.

27:08.070 --> 27:08.910
These two

27:09.590 --> 27:10.420
are in a relationship.

27:11.350 --> 27:12.500
-Really?
-Great!

27:13.170 --> 27:14.500
That's wonderful.

27:14.520 --> 27:16.840
I'm really not being a Monday morning quarterback.

27:16.870 --> 27:18.460
The first time I saw them,

27:18.780 --> 27:20.300
I knew they'd end up together.

27:21.180 --> 27:22.940
The feeling was really strong.

27:23.720 --> 27:25.000
How long have you two known each other?

27:25.290 --> 27:26.290
Almost 10 years.

27:26.310 --> 27:27.590
10 years?

27:28.970 --> 27:30.970
I knew it 10 years ago.

27:30.990 --> 27:31.910
Really?

27:31.910 --> 27:32.460
Really.

27:32.460 --> 27:34.020
Why would I lie to you? Pour the wine.

27:34.650 --> 27:35.350
How about this?

27:35.350 --> 27:38.070
Today, for this good news of yours,

27:38.660 --> 27:39.570
each of us

27:40.240 --> 27:41.910
must have a drink, okay?

27:41.940 --> 27:42.920
Mr. Shen, I won't drink.

27:42.940 --> 27:43.990
Let me pour the wine for you.

27:44.020 --> 27:44.610
Why?

27:44.660 --> 27:45.310
You have to drink.

27:45.310 --> 27:46.260
Why aren't you drinking?

27:46.260 --> 27:47.620
I have to clean up the mess afterward.

27:47.780 --> 27:49.820
You're in our house. you don't need to do that.

27:49.870 --> 27:50.520
Just drink.

27:50.550 --> 27:51.110
Yes.

27:51.180 --> 27:53.550
Alright, then I'll just drink a little.

27:53.570 --> 27:54.240
Just drink a little.

27:54.270 --> 27:55.080
It's fine.

27:55.660 --> 27:57.720
Today, I can drink

27:57.830 --> 27:59.420
because of you two.

28:01.150 --> 28:01.840
Come on.

28:01.870 --> 28:02.750
Come on.

28:03.220 --> 28:04.260
Welcome.

28:04.280 --> 28:05.150
Cheers.

28:05.150 --> 28:06.180
Thank you.

28:06.180 --> 28:07.180
Thank you, Mr. and Mrs. Shen.

28:07.180 --> 28:08.070
Thank you.

28:12.960 --> 28:14.000
You drank it all?

28:14.020 --> 28:14.650
Then let me...

28:14.680 --> 28:15.530
Come on.

28:16.030 --> 28:17.100
It was this kid showing his sincerity.

28:17.120 --> 28:17.680
Kid,

28:18.110 --> 28:20.000
show your sincerity more often.

28:22.480 --> 28:24.080
Why doesn't Mrs. Shen let me drink?

28:24.100 --> 28:25.450
She's afraid that after I get drunk,

28:25.480 --> 28:27.250
I might start reciting in English, and she won't understand.

28:30.350 --> 28:31.630
Here, Xiangya,

28:31.700 --> 28:32.870
this is for both of you.

28:32.870 --> 28:33.500
Thank you.

28:33.500 --> 28:34.500
Congratulations.

28:34.830 --> 28:35.870
[Housekeeping]

29:46.070 --> 29:46.860
Xifan,

29:47.980 --> 29:49.110
it's been a year since we parted,

29:50.200 --> 29:51.810
and you've grown to like woody scents.

29:53.190 --> 29:54.430
I still like you.

29:56.980 --> 29:58.270
But the fragrance in the sachet

29:59.750 --> 30:00.870
will eventually fade.

30:22.520 --> 30:24.480
This is from your favorite salon brand.

30:25.560 --> 30:27.720
I had them customize this perfume for you

30:28.510 --> 30:30.220
and am giving you the exclusive formula.

30:31.630 --> 30:32.830
Just to prove

30:33.740 --> 30:35.220
you are my one and only.

31:37.120 --> 31:38.390
I don't like perfume anymore.

31:39.590 --> 31:40.410
I don't even remember

31:40.430 --> 31:42.530
the last time I wore it.

31:44.040 --> 31:45.080
Some people say

31:45.480 --> 31:47.430
a fragrance represents a person.

31:48.770 --> 31:49.600
Well,

31:50.310 --> 31:51.260
the past me

31:52.330 --> 31:53.730
should have been very far

31:53.750 --> 31:54.740
from the present me.

31:55.700 --> 31:57.410
So far that I've already forgotten her.

31:58.790 --> 32:01.030
It's just that I always looked back,

32:01.500 --> 32:02.740
so I didn't notice.

32:05.700 --> 32:06.740
Let the past me

32:07.510 --> 32:08.830
stay here.

32:10.290 --> 32:11.500
The present me

32:11.920 --> 32:13.980
should go and find the person who has always been by my side,

32:15.620 --> 32:16.470
immediately.

32:16.500 --> 32:20.890
[Spring]

33:22.400 --> 33:23.320
Why are you here?

33:27.700 --> 33:28.570
I...

33:31.680 --> 33:32.680
Do you need me to do something?

33:37.430 --> 33:37.950
You...

33:38.670 --> 33:40.120
I was just about to throw out the trash.

33:40.150 --> 33:41.280
I'll go with you.

33:43.180 --> 33:43.790
Okay.

33:48.320 --> 33:48.970
Let's go.

34:23.550 --> 34:24.710
Let me send you home.

34:32.580 --> 34:33.190
I...

34:33.840 --> 34:35.120
My sachet

34:35.350 --> 34:36.750
has no scent anymore.

34:37.540 --> 34:39.330
Can you get me a new one?

34:40.380 --> 34:41.590
You suddenly came to me

34:41.750 --> 34:42.940
just for this?

34:50.880 --> 34:51.730
Actually...

34:52.150 --> 34:52.940
He Suye...

34:57.980 --> 34:58.750
He Suye,

34:59.940 --> 35:00.830
I like you.

35:02.560 --> 35:04.040
If you're still willing,

35:05.370 --> 35:06.790
can you be my boyfriend?

35:35.550 --> 35:36.580
Have you thought it through?

35:41.780 --> 35:42.710
Yes.

35:44.740 --> 35:46.050
So...

35:46.230 --> 35:46.750
do you...

35:47.100 --> 35:50.470
♫No fear of the night, no matter how long♫

35:50.910 --> 35:54.300
♫Your voice is always gentle♫

35:54.720 --> 35:58.460
♫Knowing you'll wait for me to take that brave step♫

35:58.560 --> 36:00.770
♫Walking toward you♫

36:00.790 --> 36:04.230
♫At the end of my dreams♫

36:04.420 --> 36:08.230
♫Holding on tight, never letting go♫

36:08.520 --> 36:11.670
♫Waiting for you♫

36:12.000 --> 36:15.380
♫To heal every tomorrow for me♫

36:15.480 --> 36:19.140
♫The best time♫

36:19.860 --> 36:21.270
I'm 32 years old.

36:21.690 --> 36:23.400
Do we really need to start from holding hands?

36:23.920 --> 36:27.570
♫I'm willing to be with you♫

36:27.840 --> 36:31.390
♫I'll go through every time and space with you♫

36:31.640 --> 36:36.180
♫And you are the reason♫

36:36.210 --> 36:39.490
♫I hold on to the moment so dearly♫

36:40.200 --> 36:43.940
♫No fear of the night, no matter how long♫

36:44.260 --> 36:47.760
♫Your voice is always gentle♫

36:48.030 --> 36:51.800
♫Knowing you'll wait for me to take that brave step♫

36:51.830 --> 36:53.400
♫Walking toward you♫

36:53.420 --> 36:56.470
♫The best time♫

36:58.890 --> 36:59.850
After you.

37:00.060 --> 37:00.710
Okay.

37:08.310 --> 37:09.470
What size shoes do you wear?

37:10.950 --> 37:13.760
I can wear either size 6.5 or 7.

37:15.150 --> 37:15.940
Got it.

37:19.330 --> 37:21.260
After you change your shoes, you can sit in the living room for a while.

37:21.510 --> 37:22.500
I need to change my shoes too.

37:22.670 --> 37:23.420
Okay.

37:24.570 --> 37:25.210
I'll go then.

38:15.130 --> 38:16.090
Why are you here?

38:41.230 --> 38:42.940
Why did you make so many of them?

38:46.350 --> 38:47.420
Before,

38:48.230 --> 38:50.190
whenever I thought about it, I would make one.

38:51.460 --> 38:53.340
I just never had the chance to give them out.

38:59.390 --> 39:00.390
He Suye.

39:02.240 --> 39:03.200
I'm sorry.

39:03.990 --> 39:05.600
I must have made you wait a long time.

39:06.640 --> 39:08.450
No. Don't overthink it.

39:15.200 --> 39:16.990
You can throw away the old one.

39:17.140 --> 39:18.290
It doesn't have any scent left.

39:19.440 --> 39:21.880
Also, it has acorus calamus leaves in it,

39:22.250 --> 39:23.250
which calm the mind and open the senses.

39:23.840 --> 39:25.990
You don't need it now, do you?

39:26.310 --> 39:29.230
I'm not throwing it away. It's too meaningful.

39:30.310 --> 39:31.270
Besides,

39:32.940 --> 39:35.150
Besides, the acorus calamus leaves really worked.

39:36.140 --> 39:37.180
If I had known,

39:38.060 --> 39:39.890
I would have asked you to put in more.

39:41.700 --> 39:43.060
I can't put in too much of them.

39:43.270 --> 39:43.940
You can.

39:44.800 --> 39:46.550
If you had put in more back then,

39:47.200 --> 39:48.390
maybe

39:48.950 --> 39:51.240
I would have come to my senses earlier.

39:55.670 --> 39:56.590
Look.

39:57.590 --> 39:59.420
Even my sense of smell knows

40:00.130 --> 40:02.090
that I've fallen in love with you long ago.

40:02.980 --> 40:04.500
But why did I

40:05.570 --> 40:07.430
only realize it today?

40:13.030 --> 40:13.760
It's okay.

40:15.940 --> 40:16.690
It's not too late.

40:17.870 --> 40:19.080
Now is just the right time.

40:25.710 --> 40:26.500
In my eyes,

40:27.660 --> 40:28.970
every day

40:30.090 --> 40:32.690
you get better and more deserving of love

40:33.310 --> 40:34.330
than the last.

40:36.190 --> 40:36.910
So,

40:37.980 --> 40:39.060
from now on,

40:39.760 --> 40:41.350
just focus on loving yourself.

40:42.640 --> 40:43.560
As for the rest,

40:44.370 --> 40:45.320
leave it to me.

41:01.800 --> 41:09.330
♫So I wait and wander, but the outcome isn't so bad♫

41:09.380 --> 41:16.790
♫Sparrows gather on the windowsill, sunlight streaming through♫

41:17.090 --> 41:24.840
♫Poets keep altering words to record the fast-changing world♫

41:25.030 --> 41:32.230
♫A relationship or an accident♫

41:32.720 --> 41:36.320
♫It became brighter because of you♫

41:36.440 --> 41:40.380
♫The world suddenly became so cute♫

41:40.410 --> 41:44.120
♫Maybe I'm too slow to understand♫

41:44.150 --> 41:47.890
♫I can't confess my passionate love to you♫

41:48.070 --> 41:51.880
♫Love is an admiration for beauty♫

41:51.910 --> 41:55.800
♫I've decided to only love you♫

41:55.830 --> 41:57.830
♫My foolishness♫

41:57.850 --> 41:59.690
♫My sincerity♫

41:59.720 --> 42:01.720
♫Only for one person♫

42:04.660 --> 42:10.200
♫Because of you, everything brightens up♫
